\begin_layout Section
Introduction
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The aim of this project is to monitor signal obtained from a real sensor
 thanks to a web application in order to fulfill the Internet of Things
 (IoT) concept.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This particular project will use a DHT sensor to monitor humidity and temperatur
e of the environment.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The user will be able to interact with the system and to chose different
 types of visualizations (charts, gauges and table) of the data obtained
 by the sensor.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The system will also be able to work offline, even when the sensor is not
 connected.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Finnally, the solution should have been compared to the solution on the
 ThingsBoard platform, unfortunately, an incident occured ( 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec:ThingsBoard-comparaison-(failed)"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 ).
\end_layout

